kapan pegawai Sonata Cafe masuk?

960
01:40:07,002 --> 01:40:10,422
Biasanya ada dua atau tiga orang
di kantornya.

961
01:40:14,927 --> 01:40:19,598
Apa, secara kebetulan,
kau kenal Nick Nightingale?

962
01:40:19,682 --> 01:40:22,601
Saat ini dia bermain piano di sana.

963
01:40:22,935 --> 01:40:24,395
Nick Nightingale?

964
01:40:24,853 --> 01:40:27,439
Ya, dia pernah datang ke sini.

965
01:40:30,234 --> 01:40:33,028
Mungkin kau bisa menolongku,

966
01:40:33,237 --> 01:40:36,865
sebab aku harus menghubunginya.

967
01:40:38,117 --> 01:40:39,785
Kau tahu dia menginap di mana?

968
01:40:43,497 --> 01:40:46,625
Kurasa dia tak mau
kuberi tahu kau alamatnya.

969
01:40:46,792 --> 01:40:49,128
Tak apa-apa, aku seorang dokter.

970
01:40:49,461 --> 01:40:51,922
Sebenarnya, aku teman lamanya.

971
01:40:53,507 --> 01:40:55,009
Dokter...

972
01:40:57,469 --> 01:41:01,140
dia akan tampil malam ini.
Apa kau tak bisa menunggu?

973
01:41:02,850 --> 01:41:06,061
Terus terang saja...

974
01:41:08,355 --> 01:41:10,107
ini masalah medis.

975
01:41:10,524 --> 01:41:14,820
Ada beberapa tes.
Aku tahu dia ingin tahu secepatnya.

976
01:41:42,014 --> 01:41:43,015
Permisi.

977
01:41:44,683 --> 01:41:46,935
Hai! Ada yang bisa kubantu?

978
01:41:47,186 --> 01:41:50,898
Bisa tolong hubungi
kamar Tn. Nick Nightingale?

979
01:41:51,440 --> 01:41:54,276
Maaf, Pak, Tn. Nightingale
sudah mendaftar keluar.

980
01:41:55,277 --> 01:41:58,155
- Dia sudah mendaftar keluar?
- Ya.

981
01:42:00,908 --> 01:42:04,828
- Apa dia meninggalkan alamat tujuan?
- Tidak.

982
01:42:06,205 --> 01:42:07,998
Kapan dia mendaftar keluar?

983
01:42:09,458 --> 01:42:11,460
Sekitar pukul 05.00 pagi ini.

984
01:42:11,668 --> 01:42:13,420
- Pukul 05.00?
- Ya.

985
01:42:14,713 --> 01:42:16,715
Pagi sekali, ya?

986
01:42:16,882 --> 01:42:19,676
Ya, memang agak pagi.

987
01:42:20,761 --> 01:42:22,388
Begini...

988
01:42:23,764 --> 01:42:26,642
apa kau perhatikan sesuatu...

989
01:42:27,017 --> 01:42:28,435
entahlah...

990
01:42:29,144 --> 01:42:31,772
ada yang aneh saat dia keluar?

991
01:42:34,191 --> 01:42:35,567
Aneh?

992
01:42:37,236 --> 01:42:40,197
- Kau bukan polisi, bukan?
- Bukan.

993
01:42:40,739 --> 01:42:42,116
Bukan, aku teman lamanya.

994
01:42:42,324 --> 01:42:43,409
Benarkah?

995
01:42:43,867 --> 01:42:45,369
Aku seorang dokter.

996
01:42:48,747 --> 01:42:53,085
- Bill?
- Ya.

997
01:42:55,421 --> 01:42:58,340
Lucu kau menanyakan hal itu, Bill,

998
01:42:58,549 --> 01:43:01,927
sebab memang ada yang aneh

999
01:43:02,094 --> 01:43:04,638
soal cara Tn. Nightingale pergi.

1000
01:43:04,972 --> 01:43:07,349
Sungguh? Apa itu?

1001
01:43:15,524 --> 01:43:20,112
Dia datang pagi ini, pukul 04.30

1002
01:43:20,612 --> 01:43:22,531
bersama dua pria.

1003
01:43:23,615 --> 01:43:25,284
Berbadan besar.

1004
01:43:25,784 --> 01:43:28,787
Pakaiannya rapi dan amat santun.

1005
01:43:28,996 --> 01:43:32,666
Tapi kau tak mau macam-macam
dengan mereka,

1006
01:43:32,875 --> 01:43:34,668
jika kau tahu maksudku.

1007
01:43:37,463 --> 01:43:38,964
Lalu...

1008
01:43:40,257 --> 01:43:45,012
kulihat ada memar di pipi Tn. Nightingale.

1009
01:43:45,804 --> 01:43:50,642
Terus terang, dia tampak ketakutan.

1010
01:43:51,643 --> 01:43:52,853
Ketakutan?

1011
01:43:53,020 --> 01:43:54,354
Ya.

1012
01:43:55,606 --> 01:43:57,232
Dia bilang dia ingin mendaftar keluar.

1013
01:43:57,441 --> 01:44:01,320
Lalu dia ke kamarnya
bersama salah satu pria itu.

1014
01:44:01,653 --> 01:44:05,532
Pria satunya menunggu di lobi
dan membayar tagihannya.

1015
01:44:06,241 --> 01:44:10,454
Saat mereka kembali, Tn. Nightingale
coba memberiku amplop.

1016
01:44:10,662 --> 01:44:12,372
Tapi mereka melihatnya dan mengambilnya,

1017
01:44:12,581 --> 01:44:15,501
lalu dia bilang
jika ada surat atau pesan untuknya

1018
01:44:15,709 --> 01:44:20,297
akan diambil orang yang berkepentingan.

1019
01:44:21,131 --> 01:44:23,050
Lalu mereka membawanya ke mobil.

1020
01:44:24,927 --> 01:44:27,221
Kau tahu mereka ke mana?

1021
01:44:27,679 --> 01:44:29,556
Entahlah.

1022
01:44:34,561 --> 01:44:39,107
Omong-omong...

1023
01:44:41,693 --> 01:44:43,403
Kuhargai bantuanmu.

1024
01:44:44,029 --> 01:44:46,782
Sama-sama, Bill. Dah.

1025
01:45:21,775 --> 01:45:26,071
- Dokter yang baik!
- Tuan Milich.

1026
01:45:26,238 --> 01:45:31,201
- Pakaianmu berhasil?
- Ya. Terima kasih.

1027
01:45:31,702 --> 01:45:33,078
Bagus.

1028
01:45:33,245 --> 01:45:38,208
Tuksedo. Jubah. Sepatu.

1029
01:45:40,836 --> 01:45:44,590
Kurasa kau lupa topengnya.

1030
01:45:45,882 --> 01:45:48,176
- Tak ada di sana?
- Tidak.

1031
01:45:48,343 --> 01:45:50,846
Mungkin tertinggal di pestanya?

1032
01:45:55,934 --> 01:45:57,519
Kurasa tidak.

1033
01:45:59,479 --> 01:46:02,983
Topengnya pasti hilang.
Bisa tambahkan saja ke bonnya?

1034
01:46:03,191 --> 01:46:04,192
Tentu.

1035
01:46:08,530 --> 01:46:10,449
Ini dia.

1036
01:46:11,950 --> 01:46:16,038
Semuanya $150 untuk sewanya,
$200 untuk masalahku,

1037
01:46:16,246 --> 01:46:19,666
$25 untuk topengnya. Maaf...

1038
01:46:22,461 --> 01:46:24,129
Semuanya $375.

1039
01:46:26,798 --> 01:46:28,008
Ya, Sayang?

1040
01:46:28,383 --> 01:46:29,843
Kemarilah.

1041
01:46:31,136 --> 01:46:34,056
Bisa sapa dr. Harford?

1042
01:46:35,265 --> 01:46:37,684
- Halo.
- Halo.

1043
01:46:43,357 --> 01:46:46,985
Terima kasih, Tn. Milich.
Aku akan segera meneleponmu. Dah.

1044
01:46:47,152 --> 01:46:48,987
Dah, Tuan-tuan.

1045
01:46:49,321 --> 01:46:52,574
- Selamat Natal dan Tahun Baru!
- Untukmu juga.

1046
01:46:53,492 --> 01:46:55,786
Dokter Harford...

1047
01:46:57,037 --> 01:46:58,622
ini tanda terimanya.

1048
01:46:59,956 --> 01:47:02,209
Kusobek tanda sewamu...

1049
01:47:03,377 --> 01:47:05,712
dan terima kasih telah menyewa.

1050
01:47:10,258 --> 01:47:13,804
Tuan Milich, semalam...

1051
01:47:16,348 --> 01:47:18,850
kau hendak menelepon polisi.

1052
01:47:20,310 --> 01:47:24,439
Keadaan berubah.
Kami memiliki kesepakatan lain.

1053
01:47:24,648 --> 01:47:29,569
Lalu, jika dokter yang baik
ingin sesuatu...

1054
01:47:30,237 --> 01:47:31,988
apa pun itu...

1055
01:47:32,948 --> 01:47:35,534
di sini tak hanya ada kostum.

1056
01:48:02,978 --> 01:48:04,229
Masuk.

1057
01:48:05,981 --> 01:48:08,734
- Salad tuna dan kopi pahit.
- Terima kasih.

1058
01:48:09,776 --> 01:48:12,863
Bagaimana janji temuku sore ini?

1059
01:48:13,071 --> 01:48:17,993
Hanya Ny. Akerly pukul 14.30
dan Ny. Kominski pukul 16.00.

1060
01:48:18,368 --> 01:48:22,581
Aku ada urusan mendadak,
dan aku tak bisa menemui mereka.

1061
01:48:22,789 --> 01:48:26,501
Tanya dr. Miller apa dia bisa periksa.
Jika tidak, minta maaf saja

1062
01:48:26,710 --> 01:48:28,628
- dan buat janji temu baru.
- Baik.

1063
01:48:29,045 --> 01:48:33,133
Tolong telepon garasi
dan keluarkan mobilku 30 menit lagi.

1064
01:48:33,341 --> 01:48:34,968
- Baiklah.
- Baik?

1065
01:51:20,508 --> 01:51:22,594
DOKTER WILLIAM HARFORD

1066
01:51:29,601 --> 01:51:33,438
Hentikan pertanyaanmu yang tak berguna itu

1067
01:51:33,688 --> 01:51:36,733
dan anggap surat ini
sebagai peringatan kedua.

1068
01:51:36,942 --> 01:51:40,946
Kami harap, demi kebaikanmu,
surat ini cukup.

1069
01:52:16,773 --> 01:52:19,401
- Hai.
- Hai, Ayah.

1070
01:52:20,652 --> 01:52:21,945
Hai.

1071
01:52:24,489 --> 01:52:27,158
Ada telepon untukku?

1072
01:52:27,367 --> 01:52:31,329
Dokter Sanders dan Ny. Shapiro.

1073
01:52:32,622 --> 01:52:34,374
- Hai, Semuanya.
- Hai, Ayah.

1074
01:52:34,541 --> 01:52:35,792
Hai.

1075
01:52:35,959 --> 01:52:37,919
Lihat, jawabanku benar semua.

1076
01:52:38,128 --> 01:52:40,463
- Semuanya benar?
- Ya.

1077
01:52:40,630 --> 01:52:42,382
Semuanya?

1078
01:52:42,799 --> 01:52:44,134
Bagus sekali.

1079
01:52:44,342 --> 01:52:45,844
Kau lapar?

1080
01:52:47,012 --> 01:52:48,346
Lumayan.

1081
01:52:48,513 --> 01:52:50,348
Mau makan pukul 19.00?

1082
01:52:50,515 --> 01:52:52,851
Pukul 19.00? Bisa dipercepat?

1083
01:52:53,018 --> 01:52:57,022
Aku ada janji temu di kantor.

1084
01:52:57,188 --> 01:52:59,274
Kau harus pergi lagi malam ini?

1085
01:52:59,482 --> 01:53:00,483
Kurasa begitu.

1086
01:53:00,692 --> 01:53:04,195
Ayah, apakah aku akan mendapat
anak anjing saat Natal?

1087
01:53:04,821 --> 01:53:07,282
Lihat saja nanti, ya?

1088
01:53:09,826 --> 01:53:11,995
Ia bisa menjadi anjing penjaga...

1089
01:53:12,203 --> 01:53:13,621
Kita lihat nanti.

1090
01:53:13,830 --> 01:53:16,624
Ayo, Sayang, kita selesaikan.

1091
01:53:16,833 --> 01:53:20,462
Kini ada Joe. Joe punya $2,50.

1092
01:53:20,670 --> 01:53:25,258
Lalu Mike punya $1,75.

1093
01:53:25,550 --> 01:53:29,179
Joe punya uang lebih
berapa banyak daripada Mike?

1094
01:53:29,387 --> 01:53:31,723
Lebih $0,75?

1095
01:53:33,600 --> 01:53:37,062
Berarti itu pengurangan atau penambahan?

1096
01:53:40,732 --> 01:53:44,069
"Berapa lagi" berarti itu pengurangan.

1097
01:53:44,235 --> 01:53:47,238
Ya, sebab kau akan mengambil...
Benar.

1098
01:53:47,572 --> 01:53:50,867
<i>Lalu ada orang-orang di sekeliling kami.</i>

1099
01:53:51,242 --> 01:53:53,703
<i>Jumlahnya ratusan, ada di mana-mana.</i>

1100
01:53:54,245 --> 01:53:56,414
<i>Semuanya sedang bercinta.</i>

1101
01:53:57,415 --> 01:54:00,960
<i>Lalu aku...
Aku bercinta dengan pria lain.</i>

1102
01:54:02,253 --> 01:54:03,880
<i>Banyak sekali...</i>

1103
01:54:04,422 --> 01:54:07,300
<i>entah berapa banyak
yang bercinta denganku.</i>

1104
01:55:12,824 --> 01:55:13,825
Halo.

1105
01:55:15,660 --> 01:55:16,661
<i>Halo?</i>

1106
01:55:19,497 --> 01:55:20,582
Halo?

1107
01:55:44,814 --> 01:55:47,567
Simpan kembaliannya. Selamat Natal.

1108
01:56:18,097 --> 01:56:20,517
- Ada apa?
- Domino?

1109
01:56:20,892 --> 01:56:22,727
Dia tak ada.

1110
01:56:26,731 --> 01:56:28,441
Apa kau menunggunya pulang?

1111
01:56:29,150 --> 01:56:30,652
Tidak.

1112
01:56:34,531 --> 01:56:36,115
Baiklah.

1113
01:56:37,242 --> 01:56:40,370
Kubawakan sesuatu untuknya.
Boleh kutitipkan padamu?

1114
01:56:41,579 --> 01:56:42,914
Sebentar.

1115
01:56:49,921 --> 01:56:51,756
Boleh kutanya ini dari siapa?

1116
01:56:53,258 --> 01:56:55,593
Katakan saja ini dari...

1117
01:56:56,636 --> 01:56:57,637
Bill.

1118
01:56:58,179 --> 01:57:00,890
- Kau Bill?
- Ya.

1119
01:57:01,057 --> 01:57:05,103
Bill itu?
Kau dokter yang ke sini semalam?

1120
01:57:06,104 --> 01:57:08,565
Kurasa begitu.

1121
01:57:08,940 --> 01:57:11,192
Domino bilang kau baik sekali.

1122
01:57:12,485 --> 01:57:13,611
Benarkah?

1123
01:57:16,447 --> 01:57:18,449
Bisa kau masuk?

1124
01:57:21,494 --> 01:57:22,537
Tentu.

1125
01:57:43,308 --> 01:57:44,809
Aku Sally.

1126
01:57:45,560 --> 01:57:47,437
Halo, Sally.

1127
01:57:50,481 --> 01:57:55,445
Kau tahu kapan Domino pulang?

1128
01:57:56,821 --> 01:57:58,323
Tidak.

1129
01:57:59,032 --> 01:58:00,992
Aku tak tahu.

1130
01:58:01,909 --> 01:58:05,204
- Kau tak tahu?
- Tidak.

1131
01:58:09,417 --> 01:58:14,339
