dia mungkin tak akan kembali.

1132
01:58:16,633 --> 01:58:19,427
Dia mungkin tak akan kembali?

1133
01:58:33,524 --> 01:58:35,068
Ya...

1134
01:58:40,156 --> 01:58:41,366
Aku...

1135
01:58:44,786 --> 01:58:45,912
Kau?

1136
01:58:46,204 --> 01:58:50,541
Kurasa ada sesuatu yang harus kuberi tahu.

1137
01:58:50,958 --> 01:58:53,503
- Benarkah?
- Ya.

1138
01:58:53,920 --> 01:58:56,714
Tapi aku tak tahu. Entahlah.

1139
01:58:56,881 --> 01:59:00,176
Kau tak tahu? Ada apa?

1140
01:59:04,222 --> 01:59:06,557
Aku tak tahu apakah harus
memberitahumu hal ini.

1141
01:59:12,230 --> 01:59:15,066
Kau mau duduk?

1142
01:59:15,775 --> 01:59:17,527
Silakan duduk.

1143
01:59:33,668 --> 01:59:38,047
- Aku tak tahu cara mengatakannya.
- Kau tak tahu?

1144
01:59:42,427 --> 01:59:46,222
Karena kau di sini
bersama Domino semalam...

1145
01:59:48,766 --> 01:59:53,187
kurasa akan adil jika kuberi tahu kau...

1146
01:59:56,274 --> 01:59:59,610
dia mendapat hasil pagi ini...

1147
01:59:59,777 --> 02:00:03,072
dan hasilnya HIV positif.

1148
02:00:14,083 --> 02:00:17,003
- HIV positif?
- Ya.

1149
02:00:31,392 --> 02:00:36,272
Aku amat sedih mendengarnya.

1150
02:00:40,818 --> 02:00:42,195
Ya.

1151
02:00:43,488 --> 02:00:46,449
Itu amat menyedihkan.

1152
02:00:59,504 --> 02:01:02,215
Boleh kutawarkan sesuatu?

1153
02:01:02,715 --> 02:01:04,675
Mungkin secangkir kopi?

1154
02:01:13,267 --> 02:01:14,727
Tidak usah, terima kasih.

1155
02:01:19,524 --> 02:01:21,025
Kurasa...

1156
02:01:22,401 --> 02:01:24,362
sebaiknya aku pergi.

1157
02:01:28,783 --> 02:01:30,952
Baik.

1158
02:03:13,220 --> 02:03:14,847
- Taksi!
- Sedang istirahat.

1159
02:05:04,665 --> 02:05:07,710
Aku minta cappucino.

1160
02:05:07,918 --> 02:05:09,754
Akan kuantar.

1161
02:05:09,920 --> 02:05:11,047
Terima kasih.

1162
02:05:49,835 --> 02:05:54,882
MANTAN RATU KECANTIKAN
OVERDOSIS DI KAMAR HOTEL

1163
02:06:49,728 --> 02:06:51,021
INFORMASI

