1169
02:07:05,369 --> 02:07:07,913
Curran. Amanda Curran.

1170
02:07:08,122 --> 02:07:10,332
C-U-R-R-A-N?

1171
02:07:11,750 --> 02:07:12,626
Ya.

1172
02:07:14,920 --> 02:07:16,755
Nona Amanda Curran?

1173
02:07:17,548 --> 02:07:18,883
Benar.

1174
02:07:19,550 --> 02:07:23,053
Maaf, Dokter.
Nona Curran meninggal sore ini.

1175
02:07:27,099 --> 02:07:28,976
Dia meninggal sore ini?

1176
02:07:29,351 --> 02:07:32,688
Ya, pukul 15.45.

1177
02:07:33,147 --> 02:07:34,607
Aku turut berdukacita.

1178
02:08:22,780 --> 02:08:25,449
<i>Sebab mungkin aku bisa tewas...</i>

1179
02:08:26,367 --> 02:08:28,410
<i>dan begitu juga kau.</i>

1180
02:10:12,014 --> 02:10:13,015
Halo.

1181
02:10:14,266 --> 02:10:16,060
Ya, ini dr. Harford.

1182
02:10:18,228 --> 02:10:19,521
Malam ini?

1183
02:10:20,230 --> 02:10:22,358
Tidak, tak apa-apa.

1184
02:10:26,403 --> 02:10:30,115
Tolong beri tahu dia
aku akan datang 20 menit lagi. Ya?

